<h1>Query</h1>
<p>This tab allows you to edit and create <a href="../../alvao-asset-management/searching/query">
database queries</a>.<br/>
The query text is displayed on the left. It can be edited directly, but you need to know the <a href="../../alvao-asset-management/searching/query#query-language">
Query language syntax</a>.</p>
<p>Options:</p>
	<ul>
 <li><strong>Evaluate</strong> - evaluate the query and display the result in a print report.</li>
 <li><strong>Create a new query</strong> - create <a href="query-wizard-1">
 new query using the wizard</a>.</li>
 <li><strong>Load</strong> - load the query from a file.</li>
 <li><strong>Save</strong> - save the query to a file.</li>
	</ul>
</asp:Content>
